# AI Model Deployment with Docker and Kubernetes
Developing Basic Flower Image Classification AI model for deployment with docker and Kubernetes. 
Used the Google Apis flower image dataset to train my model.

## Setup Instructions:

Step 1: Develop the AI Model
  -> Install all the required packages included in the "Requirements.txt" file.

Step 2: Run Flask App:
  -> python webapp.py

Step 3: Set up a Deployment Pipeline
  -> Create a Dockerfile
  -> Build Docker Image using the command:
        " docker build -t kushmanda_Task . "

  -> Run the Docker container locally:
        "docker run -p 5000:5000 kushmanda_Task"

Step 4: Kubernetes Deployment
  -> Deploy to Kubernetes using the command:
        "kubectl apply -f my-kubernete.yaml"



